{"tid":1689237,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟用幾分鐘 幫下今日比狗咬嘅消防哥哥","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:11:12.000Z","uid":211994,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c19887770d584ee94ba72b6b831d642b09459bef","tid":1689237,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"（手動轉）<br />\n//落車同防暴理論嗰位消防師兄宜家俾好多藍絲追擊同起底。甚至動員寫信投訴，亦有傳佢比高層照肺。<br />\n麻煩大家花啲啲寫信去消防處總部，讚揚呢個消防員盡忠職守。<br />\n<br />\n我朋友話當時金鐘消防員開閘單野，消防收左70000封信。好彩支持的比投訴的多好多。<br />\n消防為我地撐左好耐，宜家係時候報恩。<br />\n消防處好重視民意，如果多人寫信/電郵去讚佢，消防處真係可能為免激起民憤而放生佢！<br />\n<br />\n標題：表揚及慰問在11月2日於中環執勤時被警方粗暴對待的消防員<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n消防設備是救災救人的重要工具，時刻檢查及確保消防設備的完好是一個消防員的專業職責。然而11月2日一名消防人員在中環出勤執行職務期間，所駕駛的消防車被警隊的催淚彈擊中，消防員馬上下車了解情況時並向在場警員表達意見。<br />\n讓人始料不及的是，在場的數十名警務人員非但未有為事件致歉，更呼喝、挑釁、推撞、圍堵在場的唯一一名消防員，事件讓人震驚及憤怒。<br />\n在場警員甚至馬上驅逐在場的記者朋友，令消防人員陷入孤立無援的境地，情況相當危急。<br />\n<br />\n在此，本人希望向這位消防人表達謝意及深切慰問！同時希望消防局不要因為政治壓力，扭曲消防員的守責行為。如此方不負社會對消防之期望！<br />\n<br />\n       此致<br />\n消防處長<br />\n<br />\n市民XXX<br />\n2019年11月3日<br />\n<br />\nsend email去消防處總部：<br />\nhkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#weconnect消防<br />\n#standwith消防<br />\n#有無手足可以幫手做文宣<br />\n#麻煩廣傳求推爆 //"},{"pid":"d6b737a36900261b1fde22f4d331c328516892de","tid":1689237,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"一人一信支持消防哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4760dffd86c3554dcd51c76e827ffc6757c280","tid":1689237,"uid":287130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c0bc2c028c60b50be7606cb6fa1c56cae43b39","tid":1689237,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"b4357f5f6f6796c0c7467ec9662c6bfd3f5740db","tid":1689237,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"Sent"},{"pid":"8a115cb6f320fb8a24f2750ad0d8458d40a6dacc","tid":1689237,"uid":103591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7afe0f94ad4513f46c09de420ebdfacb42009737","tid":1689237,"uid":246757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"推啊屌你"},{"pid":"4ebf1fd5631e430af5fdeb6b0203d9d0b761fe5f","tid":1689237,"uid":246757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:51:21.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"9ea28aa125c6a3e74617b80d0368f5a79a49d534","tid":1689237,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af8680c8334f76a23acb42ff1162e0909def0520","tid":1689237,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"由近平"},{"pid":"6c725eecc64126c24bf402fa6cdf678c5eb2c91c","tid":1689237,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"2e1aee1e0bfb82dc19ce4dc16591a8a6f2d51081","tid":1689237,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:19:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"037e7964c545b1cbb465f58b5c3697ce5ccee44c","tid":1689237,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6685a31e5219080d2aa240e1c1fee145ce307981","tid